WEBVTT

00:00:03.780 --> 00:00:06.700
<v Audio Descriptions>A man is using a laptop with the text on the screen

00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:08.700
<v Audio Descriptions>being highlighted as it is spoken

00:00:08.700 --> 00:00:11.580
<v computer>"Some people can't see the text on this screen"

00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:15.520
<v computer>"fortunately computers can convert text to speech"

00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:18.500
It's technology that many people who are blind

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.500
have been relying on for years

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:22.800
<v Audio Descriptions>A service dog is next to the man

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.340
<v Audio Descriptions>He may be blind

00:00:24.340 --> 00:00:27.380
but it's also important for many people with dyslexia

00:00:27.380 --> 00:00:30.820
<v Audio Descriptions>A woman is reading on a tablet and listen with headphones

00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:34.260
and very useful for people with difficulty reading text

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:38.780
<v Audio Descriptions>A man removes his glasses and listens to a news article on his tablet

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:42.060
as well as some people who just like to multitask

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:45.600
<v Audio Descriptions>A man listens to a magazine article as they do the washing

00:00:46.300 --> 00:00:50.280
but for this to work, websites and apps need to be properly coded

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:53.520
<v Audio Descriptions>The website is not properly working for the woman with headphones

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:55.120
<v Audio Descriptions>She is frustrated

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:57.840
which has the added benefit of helping search engines

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:00.280
index websites' contents better

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:02.280
<v Audio Descriptions>The man with the service dog

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:06.260
<v Audio Descriptions>is using his mobile device outside with bone conducting headphones

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:10.620
<v Audio Descriptions>different people from earlier are seen using text-to-speech

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:12.620
Web accessibility

00:01:12.620 --> 00:01:15.800
Essential for some, useful for all.
